    <item>
      <title>청문회마다 농지법 의혹... 헌법 121조 ‘경자유전’ 어떡하나</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/2025/07/20/33TMCVS3ONG6DBZER4DTUM42F4/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/2025/07/20/33TMCVS3ONG6DBZER4DTUM42F4/</guid>
      <dc:creator>이동훈 기자</dc:creator>
